ration 8 - 10 ms in the 72-ks data. Upper\nlimits to the size distribution of TNOs at the small size end are suggested.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 May 2008 03:50:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
